&lt;/style>&lt;/head>&lt;body style=" font-family:'.SF NS Text'; font-size:13pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;">
&lt;p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;">&lt;span style=" font-family:'Helvetica'; color:#454545;">This 0.56&amp;quot; 7-segment LED display includes a driver chip for simple control via an I2C interface. The backpack features address-selection jumpers so you can connect up to eight displays on a single I2C bus.&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&lt;/body>&lt;/html></description>
